        "content": "<h2>Overview:</h2><p>This website is operated by Pawcredible. Throughout the site, the terms “we”, “us” and “our” refer to Pawcredible. Pawcredible offers this website, including all information, tools, and services available from this site to you—the user—conditioned upon your acceptance of all terms, conditions, policies, and notices stated here. By visiting our site and/or purchasing something from us, you engage in our “Service” and agree to be bound by the following Terms of Service (“Terms”), including any additional terms and conditions referenced or linked here. These Terms apply to all users of the site, including browsers, vendors, customers, and content contributors. Please read these Terms of Service carefully before using our site. By accessing any part of our website, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree to all of them, you may not access the site or use any services. We reserve the right to update, change, or replace any part of these Terms by posting updates to our website. Your continued use of our site following any updates means you accept those changes. Our store is hosted on Shopify Inc., providing the e-commerce platform that allows us to offer our products and services to you.</p><h2>Online Store Terms</h2><p>By using our store, you confirm that you are at least the age of majority in your state or province, or you have given consent for any of your minor dependents to use this site. You may not use our products for any illegal or unauthorized purpose or violate any laws in your jurisdiction. You must not transmit any harmful code such as worms or viruses. Violating these terms will result in termination of services.</p><p>If we ever ask for your information for any other reason (like sending marketing emails), we will either ask you directly for your explicit consent or offer a clear option to decline.</p><h2>General Conditions</h2><p>We reserve the right to refuse service to anyone for any reason at any time. You understand that your content (not including credit card information) may be transferred unencrypted and may involve changes to meet technical requirements. Credit card info is always encrypted. You agree not to reproduce, copy, or exploit any part of our service without written permission from us.</p><h2>Accuracy, Completeness And Timeliness Of Information</h2><p>We are not responsible if the information on our site is not accurate, complete, or current. It is meant for general guidance and should not be solely relied upon. Historical information may be present and is provided for reference only. We may update the site at any time but are not obligated to do so.</p><h2>Modifications To The Service And Prices</h2><p>Product prices may change without notice. We may change or discontinue any service or part of the website at any time without prior notice. We are not liable for any modification or suspension of services.</p><h2>Products Or Services</h2><p>Some products or services may be available only online and in limited quantities. These are subject to our return policy. We do our best to display accurate colors and images, but we can’t guarantee how they appear on every screen. We reserve the right to limit the sale of our products to any individual or location and to change descriptions or pricing at any time.</p><p>We cannot guarantee that our products or services will meet every customer’s expectations.</p><h2>Accuracy Of Billing And Account Information</h2><p>We reserve the right to refuse or cancel any order you place with us. We may limit or cancel quantities per person, household, or order. These restrictions may apply to orders under the same customer account, credit card, or billing/shipping address. If we make a change to or cancel an order, we’ll attempt to notify you using the email, billing address, or phone number you provided at checkout. You agree to provide current, complete, and accurate purchase and account details. You also agree to update your