l Information</h2><p>Your submission of personal information through the store is governed by our <a href=\"/pages/privacy-policy\" title=\"Privacy Policy\"><strong>Privacy Policy</strong></a>, which you can view on our website.</p><h2>Errors, Inaccuracies And Omissions</h2><p>Occasionally, our website or service may include typographical errors or inaccuracies relating to product descriptions, pricing, promotions, shipping costs, or availability.</p><p>We reserve the right to correct any errors and to update or cancel orders if any information on the site is inaccurate, at any time and without prior notice (even after you’ve placed an order).</p><p>We are not obligated to clarify or amend information unless required by law. Any update date listed doesn’t necessarily mean all site content has been modified.</p><h2>Prohibited Uses</h2><p>In addition to other restrictions in these Terms, you are not permitted to use our site or content:</p><ul><li>For unlawful purposes</li><li>To violate any laws or regulations</li><li>To infringe on intellectual property rights</li><li>To harass or harm others</li><li>To upload malicious code or spam</li><li>To collect or misuse others’ personal info</li><li>To bypass security features</li></ul><p>We reserve the right to terminate your access for violating these restrictions.</p><h2>Disclaimer Of Warranties; Limitation Of Liability</h2><p>We can’t guarantee uninterrupted, error-free, or secure access to our site or services. All products and services are provided “as is” and “as available.”</p><p>We don’t make warranties about the accuracy or reliability of the results from using our service.</p><p>In no case shall Pawcredible or our staff, partners, or affiliates be liable for any direct or indirect damages, including loss of profits, data, or business, even if we were advised of the possibility.</p><p>Some regions don’t allow limitation of liability, so our responsibility will be limited to the maximum allowed by law</p><h2>Indemnification</h2><p>You agree to defend, indemnify, and hold Pawcredible and our partners, employees, and affiliates harmless from any claims or demands, including legal fees, made by a third party due to your violation of these Terms or any law or third-party rights.</p><h2>Severability</h2><p>If any part of these Terms is found to be illegal or unenforceable, the rest will still remain valid & enforceable. The unenforceable portion will be removed or limited allowed by law.</p><p>Termination</p><p>These Terms remain effective unless terminated by you or us.<br/>You may end them by notifying us that you no longer wish to use our services or by stopping use of our site.<br/>We may also terminate this agreement at any time if we believe you’ve violated any terms, and you’ll remain liable for any amounts due up to the date of termination.<br/>We may also deny you access to our services if needed.</p><h2>Entire Agreement</h2><p>These Terms of Service and any related policies represent the full agreement between you and Pawcredible.<br/>They override any previous verbal or written agreements. If we don’t enforce a part of these Terms, it doesn’t mean we’re waiving our rights to enforce it in the future.</p><h2>Governing Law</h2><p>These Terms and any services we provide are governed by the laws of the region in which Pawcredible operates (e.g., your local jurisdiction or business registration region).</p><h2>Changes To Terms Of Service</h2><p>You can always find the latest version of our Terms on this page. We may update or change them at any time.<br/>Your continued use of our website or services after changes are posted means you accept the new Terms.</p><h2>Contact Information</h2><p>Questions about the Terms of Service? Please email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@pawcredible.co.uk\" title=\"mailto:support@pawcredible.co.uk\"><strong>support@pawcredible.co.uk</strong></a> — we’re happy to help!</p><h2>Handling Of Copyrighted Images And Materials</h2><p>To the best of our